title: What device is this?
content: I found this old device, but I don't know what it is.

answers_data.content:
I think it's an impedance matching device for antenna.

If you have someone in your house in the past who was engaged in amateur radio and in addition, there is such a tool:



then it is most likely.

comments.text: Ok, thank you. I don't have any other device with it, but it might be that.
